### Create a new Campaign using the automated token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Curse of Strahd",
  "description": "A gothic horror campaign set in the dark lands of Barovia."
}

### Fetch all campaigns for this user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}